Supervised Mailings plugin for Fat Free CRM

Installation Instructions:
  Install http://github.com/tractis/crm_google_account_settings

  $ ruby script/plugin installgit://github.com/tractis/crm_supervised_mailings.git
  $ ruby script/generate crm_supervised_mailings_migration
  $ rake db:migrate

At the moment this plugin is designed to work with gmail, you need to:
 - Install ruby-gmail gem [http://github.com/dcparker/ruby-gmail]
   $ sudo gem install ruby-gmail -s http://gemcutter.org
   $ net/smtp
   $ net/imap
   
   
